    "description": "BRIDGE International Group Corp., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the provision of corporate sale services in Japan. It operates through Inside Sales Outsourcing Business, Process Technology Business, and Training segments. The company offers consulting services, such as revenue process, marketing process, inside sales process, field sales process, customer success process design and optimization, as well as RevOps launch and optimization; and marketing, inside sales, and customer success field outsourcing and operations services. It also provides Tech Stack comprising Rev Tech, MarTech, Sales Tech, and Customer Tech selection, implementation, and utilization support services; and role-specific training in the sales process. The company was formerly known as BRIDGE International Corp. and changed its name to BRIDGE International Group Corp. in October 2025. BRIDGE International Group Corp. was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
